Lord, I thank you that you have given us a record of these truths.

00:42:03.840 --> 00:42:12.040
God, I pray you'd help us to understand tonight how desperately we need you.

00:42:12.040 --> 00:42:18.240
It's not enough to have goods and have plenty.

00:42:18.240 --> 00:42:20.040
Lord, we need you.

00:42:20.120 --> 00:42:26.280
As I mentioned at the end of the memorial service yesterday, as the lady sang, I'd rather

00:42:26.280 --> 00:42:27.280
