00:42:34.800 --> 00:42:39.280
What matters is that we have Jesus.

00:42:39.280 --> 00:42:43.360
I think as the songwriter said, now I belong to Jesus.

00:42:43.360 --> 00:42:45.360
Jesus belongs to me.

00:42:46.200 --> 00:42:52.560
God, I pray that you'd give us a heart and a burden for our nation, a nation that's been

00:42:52.560 --> 00:42:58.960
exposed to truth but has departed.

00:42:58.960 --> 00:43:08.560
Rejected God and your Word, Lord, I pray you'd help us to be faithful, help us to be steadfast,

00:43:08.560 --> 00:43:09.560
unmovable.

00:43:09.800 --> 00:43:19.120
Lord, help us to be used as vessels that have an impact in this lost and dying world.

00:43:19.120 --> 00:43:21.200
Help us to propagate the truth.

00:43:21.200 --> 00:43:25.120
I pray that in these few moments of invitation that you'd have your will and way, that decisions

00:43:25.120 --> 00:43:27.920
